skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: hershey guide
des:
A guide to Hershey, Pennsylvania; providing an overview and history of the city, as well as places to visit. This skill can help you get around town to see what is worth seeing, and where you can stop to relax or grab a bite to eat.

Plan a day out by learning about what attractions there are within Hershey:
 • What are the top five things to do in Hershey?
 • Where can we get something to eat?
 • How is the weather looking for today?

Learn about the history of the town and the founder, Milton S. Hershey.
 • Tell me a fact about the town of Hershey.
 • Tell me something interesting about Milton Hershey.
 • I want to know more about the chocolate factory.
 • Tell me about someone famous from Hershey.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
